org.team5940.robot_core.modules.logging

Class AbstractLoggerModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team5940.robot_core.modules.AbstractModule
      • org.team5940.robot_core.modules.logging.AbstractLoggerModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoggerModule, Module
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileLoggerModule, SystemLoggerModule

    public abstract class AbstractLoggerModule
extends AbstractModule
implements LoggerModule
    This is a abstract, reference implementation of LoggerModule that constructs the Strings to log for you.
